headline: AutoZone to hold Stockholders’ Meeting December 18, 2024
summary: MEMPHIS, Tenn., Dec. 03, 2024 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- AutoZone, Inc. (NYSE:AZO) announced it will hold its Annual Meeting of Stockholders on Wednesday, December 18, 2024, at the J.R. Hyde III Store Support Center in Memphis, Tennessee. The meeting will begin at 9:00 a.m. (ET). Additionally, this event will be webcast and can be accessed at AutoZone’s website at www.autozone.com and by clicking on Investor Relations. About AutoZone: As of August 31, 2024, the Company had 6,432 stores in the U.S., 794
